#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Cāpālavagga"
msgstr "1. At the Cāpāla Shrine"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Buddhasutta → arahantasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn51.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Buddhasutta"
msgstr "8. Awakened"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.8:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, iddhipādā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four bases of psychic power."

msgctxt "sn51.8:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn51.8:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ "
"iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.8:1.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.8:1.5"
msgid "cittasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.8:1.6"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.8:1.7"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro iddhipādā."
msgstr "These are the four bases of psychic power."

msgctxt "sn51.8:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"tathāgato ‘arahaṃ sammāsambuddho’ti vuccatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"It is because he has developed and cultivated these four bases of psychic "
"power that the Realized One is called ‘the perfected one, the fully awakened "
"Buddha’.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.8:1.9"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
